\begin{frame}{Dataset}
\small

\begin{alertblock}{Empirical design}
\scriptsize
The main data sources are WRDS and FRED. The OOS index testing is kept strictly seperated from the training data for walk-forward CV and the test set. Model selection is conducted based on the test set results.
\end{alertblock}

